{"tid":318333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★陳帆指構思中「同屋共住」或類似「七十二家房客」模式","createTime":"2017-07-12T04:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T06:34:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccda562ca41a66db9752937abb597b32e4b4c560","tid":318333,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆出席本台節目表示，現時正在構思的「同屋共住」的構想，有不同的模式，包括類似現時劏房的做法，以分間模式間出不同獨立空間，但面積及安全衛生都會較劏房好。<br />\n<br />\n另一種是類似「七十二家房客」模式，不同家庭同住一個地方，當中有自己房間，亦有共用的互動空間。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆表示，如果由非政府機構運作，就不需要受中間剝削。至於錢方面需動用社會資源，有信心有一筆大的資金，但重申長遠需要覓地興建房屋解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆說，自己的願景是希望先有「一百幾十間未劏單位」參與計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1341572-20170712.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1341572-20170712.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7zuk36%2BAJRB7bt8ZW%2Ff2xgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a376af14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1341572-20170712.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=17c41f96\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1341572-20170712.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44accd61cdff5d0e44e8d808758f70ebea8f8ef4","tid":318333,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/learntorich/1380973317-3769797157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Flearntorich%2F1380973317-3769797157.jpg&h=85ff3e76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1848dd948e5f5c503a914a2b27b13230b8704fd9","tid":318333,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkmemory.org/shaw/images/photos/Comedy02_173029op.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmemory.